# Step Wizard (`StepWizard`)

**Path:** `src/app/components/payment-pages/StepWizard.tsx`

Horizontal step indicator for the Payment Pages creation flow (and reusable for other 3-step wizards using `BuilderStep`).

## Container
- Full width, `shrink-0`
- `bg-[#fafafa]` (no bottom border)
- Padding: `px-[32px] py-5` (aligns with page content gutters)
- Inner row: `w-full mx-0`, `flex flex-wrap items-center justify-start`, `list-none` on `<ul>` (left-aligned; same content width as page body)

## Layout
- Each step: **indicator left**, **label right** (`gap-3`)
- Between steps: **dashed connector** — `border-t-2 border-dashed`, width `w-12 sm:w-20 md:w-24`, horizontal margin `mx-3 sm:mx-4`
- Connector color: `#22C55E` when the segment is completed (previous step done), else `#e0e0e0` (neutral, matches upcoming rail)

## Step states

| State | Circle | Label |
|---|---|---|
| **Completed** | Solid `#22C55E`, white Lucide `Check` (`size-[18px]`, `strokeWidth={2.5}`) | `font-semibold text-[#22C55E]` |
| **Active (in progress)** | `border-2 border-[#22C55E]`, transparent fill, step index `#22C55E`, `text-[14px] font-semibold` | `font-semibold text-[#101010]` |
| **Upcoming** | Neutral: `border-2 border-[#e0e0e0] bg-white`, step index `text-[#7e7e7e]` (no green/blue tint) | `font-medium text-[#7e7e7e]` |

- Indicators use `size-10` (`40px`), `rounded-full`; completed circle uses `shadow-sm`; active/upcoming rings have no fill tint on upcoming.

## Semantics
- Outer: `<nav aria-label="Create payment page steps">`
- Steps: `<ul>` / `<li>`; connectors use `aria-hidden`

## Integration (Payment Pages)
- Steps: Page Information → Page Builder → Additional Settings (`BuilderStep`: `info` | `builder` | `settings`)
- Mounted in: `PageInfoForm`, `PageBuilder`, `AdditionalSettings` — pass `currentStep={builderStep}`
